  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Hello, person... You are a new addition. My name is EESUIA. You spawned
    into MY world with no memories of where you''re from. So you must listen to me,
    because I would guide you. Look around and make it to the end of your adventure
    to see what awaits you next. In this game, you must go through the obby, and
    firgue out the truth. WASD works just the same, as well as arrow keys, whichever
    you prefer. Space bar is jump, and if you click on shop your arrow should disapear
    so you must click "Esc" and click shop again.


    You probably need this information...
    Good luck- you''ll need it...  Consider this a payment from what I took from
    you.


    Signed: ######'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
